Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.89,0:44:19.19,CHT,,0,0,0,,注意  不管你是誰  這個頻道僅供緊急呼叫使用\N{\rENG}Attention, whoever you are, this channel is reserved for emergency calls only.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.33,0:44:22.39,CHT,,0,0,0,,這不是玩笑  小姐!  我聽起來象在訂比薩嗎?\N{\rENG}No fucking shit, lady! Do I sound like I'm ordering a pizza?
