Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.02,0:44:44.18,CHT,,0,0,0,,他們正在鞏固陣地  而你卻和我在這兒廢話!\N{\rENG}They are fortifying their positions while you're jerkin' me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.62,0:44:48.25,CHT,,0,0,0,,先生  我已經說過了  這是一個專用頻道\N{\rENG}Sir, I've already told you. This is a reserved channel.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.39,0:44:52.12,CHT,,0,0,0,,如果有緊急情況  請你打911\N{\rENG}If this is an emergency call, dial 911 on your telephone.
