Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.76,0:45:32.16,CHT,,0,0,0,,我還以為你們只吃甜甜圈\N{\rENG}Thought you guys just ate doughnuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.23,0:45:34.96,CHT,,0,0,0,,這是給我太太買的\N{\rENG}They're for my wife.
