Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.04,0:45:40.97,CHT,,0,0,0,,包起來\N{\rENG}Bag it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.48,0:45:43.81,CHT,,0,0,0,,真會選時間\N{\rENG}Big time.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.65,0:45:48.21,CHT,,0,0,0,,謝謝\N{\rENG}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.22,0:45:53.65,CHT,,0,0,0,,中心呼叫林肯30  完畢\N{\rENG}Dispatch to 8-Lincoln-30. Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.72,0:45:55.69,CHT,,0,0,0,,我是林肯30  請講  完畢\N{\rENG}This is 8-Lincoln-30.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.79,0:46:00.06,CHT,,0,0,0,,請前往中富大廈  調查非法闖入案件\N{\rENG}Investigate a code two at Nakatomi Plaza, Century City.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.13,0:46:04.09,CHT,,0,0,0,,林肯30呼叫中心  我這就去\N{\rENG}8-Lincoln-30 to Dispatch. I'm on my way.
