Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.42,0:48:45.36,CHT,,0,0,0,,天啊!\N{\rENG}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.24,0:49:03.44,CHT,,0,0,0,,他在電梯井裡\N{\rENG}He's in the elevator shaft.
