Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.05,0:49:46.88,CHT,,0,0,0,,天啊!\N{\rENG}Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.13,0:49:54.46,CHT,,0,0,0,,我可以騙過他們  但不能讓他們聽見槍聲\N{\rENG}I can stall them, but not if they hear gunshots.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.53,0:49:57.09,CHT,,0,0,0,,把他關起來  他就無計可施了\N{\rENG}If you lock him in, he'll be neutralized...
