Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.79,0:53:46.78,CHT,,0,0,0,,埃迪\N{\rENG}Eddie?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.26,0:53:49.53,CHT,,0,0,0,,我早有預感你會呼叫我\N{\rENG}I had a feelin' you'd be callin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.05,0:54:15.65,CHT,,0,0,0,,晚上好  警官  我能幫什麼忙嗎?\N{\rENG}Evenin', officer. What can I do for you?
