Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.54,0:56:46.34,CHT,,0,0,0,,看在老天份上...\N{\rENG}Oh, for the love...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.91,0:56:51.67,CHT,,0,0,0,,林肯30呼叫中心\N{\rENG}8-Lincoln-30 to Dispatch.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.75,0:56:52.84,CHT,,0,0,0,,林肯30  請講\N{\rENG}Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.91,0:56:57.41,CHT,,0,0,0,,又白跑一趟  中富大廈一切正常  完畢\N{\rENG}A wild-goose chase at Nakatomi Plaza. Everything here's OK. Over.
