Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.23,0:57:08.96,CHT,,0,0,0,,我的天!\N{\rENG}Goddamn it! Jesus H Christ!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.04,0:57:18.73,CHT,,0,0,0,,歡迎加入派對  老兄!\N{\rENG}Welcome to the party, pal!
