Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.89,0:57:33.91,CHT,,0,0,0,,我請求立即支援!\N{\rENG}I need backup assistance now!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.26,0:57:36.55,CHT,,0,0,0,,馬上來!  聽見沒有?  馬上!\N{\rENG}Now, goddamn it! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.18,0:57:57.11,CHT,,0,0,0,,莫妮卡  我會搞定餐館預約\N{\rENG}Monica, I can get us a table.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.28,0:58:00.80,CHT,,0,0,0,,沃夫岡和我是很好的朋友\N{\rENG}Wolfgang and I are very close friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.38,0:58:03.01,CHT,,0,0,0,,我採訪過他  保證沒問題\N{\rENG}I interviewed him!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.92,0:58:07.55,CHT,,0,0,0,,重複  有員警需要增援...\N{\rENG}Repeat. Officer needs assistance at...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.69,0:58:11.35,CHT,,0,0,0,,我在中富大廈!  我的車被打成篩子啦!\N{\rENG}I'm at Nakatomi Plaza. They're turning my car into Swiss cheese!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.43,0:58:15.49,CHT,,0,0,0,,我需要支援  快點來!  他媽的  馬上!\N{\rENG}I need backup assistance now! Now, goddamn it! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.38,0:58:38.37,CHT,,0,0,0,,沒想到聽到警笛這麼高興!\N{\rENG}Never thought I'd love to hear that sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.65,0:58:43.06,CHT,,0,0,0,,大家不要緊張  只是一點麻煩  沒什麼\N{\rENG}All of you relax. This is a matter of inconvenient timing, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.16,0:58:47.92,CHT,,0,0,0,,警方的行動是不可避免的  而且是必要的\N{\rENG}Police action was inevitable... and, as it happens, necessary.
