Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.84,0:58:58.33,CHT,,0,0,0,,我想我已經說過  要保持無線電靜默\N{\rENG}I told you all I wanted radio silence until...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.41,0:59:01.84,CHT,,0,0,0,,是嗎  我很抱歉  漢斯  我沒收到這條指令\N{\rENG}I'm very sorry, Hans. I didn't get that message.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.84,0:59:04.54,CHT,,0,0,0,,也許你應該貼在公告板上\N{\rENG}Maybe you should have put it on a bulletin board.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.61,0:59:07.14,CHT,,0,0,0,,我想既然我幹掉了  托尼  馬可和他的朋友\N{\rENG}I figured since I waxed Tony and Marco and his friend here,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.21,0:59:10.05,CHT,,0,0,0,,你和卡爾還有法蘭柯  也許會感到寂寞\N{\rENG}I figured you and Karl and Franco might be lonely
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.15,0:59:12.08,CHT,,0,0,0,,所以我想和你聊聊\N{\rENG}so I wanted to give you a call.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.19,0:59:14.38,CHT,,0,0,0,,他怎麼會知道這麼多?\N{\rENG}How does he know so much about us?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.82,0:59:17.95,CHT,,0,0,0,,你真是一個好人\N{\rENG}That's very kind of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.39,0:59:21.38,CHT,,0,0,0,,我想你就是那位不速之客\N{\rENG}I assume you are our mysterious party crasher.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.06,0:59:23.43,CHT,,0,0,0,,做為一名警衛\N{\rENG}You are most troublesome
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.50,0:59:25.62,CHT,,0,0,0,,你可真是稱職\N{\rENG}for a security guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.50,0:59:28.56,CHT,,0,0,0,,抱歉  漢斯  你猜錯了\N{\rENG}Sorry, Hans. Wrong guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.64,0:59:31.40,CHT,,0,0,0,,要不要再猜一次  說不準還能得分\N{\rENG}Would you like to go for double jeopardy?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.51,0:59:38.91,CHT,,0,0,0,,這對你的健康沒好處\N{\rENG}These are very bad for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.78,0:59:41.27,CHT,,0,0,0,,你到底是誰?\N{\rENG}Who are you, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.38,0:59:43.65,CHT,,0,0,0,,我只是一隻討厭的蒼蠅  漢斯\N{\rENG}Just the fly in the ointment, Hans.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.72,0:59:45.12,CHT,,0,0,0,,一隻搗亂的猴子\N{\rENG}The monkey in the wrench,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.00,0:59:47.19,CHT,,0,0,0,,喉嚨裡的一根刺\N{\rENG}the pain in the ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.33,0:59:54.79,CHT,,0,0,0,,去查查別的人  別用對講機\N{\rENG}Check on all the others. Don't use the radio.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.90,0:59:59.06,CHT,,0,0,0,,看看馬可是不是真的死了  查出還有誰失聯\N{\rENG}See if he's lying about Marco and find out if anyone else is missing.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.67,1:00:04.73,CHT,,0,0,0,,不速之客先生?\N{\rENG}Mr Mystery Guest,
