Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.92,1:00:17.68,CHT,,0,0,0,,你給我帶來了麻煩\N{\rENG}but you have me at a loss.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.75,1:00:19.51,CHT,,0,0,0,,你知道我的名字  但是你是誰?\N{\rENG}You know my name, but who are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.62,1:00:23.75,CHT,,0,0,0,,你是不是小的時候電影看多了?\N{\rENG}Just another American who saw too many movies as a child?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.89,1:00:27.05,CHT,,0,0,0,,還是破產家庭的孤兒?\N{\rENG}Another orphan of a bankrupt culture
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.13,1:00:30.26,CHT,,0,0,0,,自以為是大英雄?  藍波?狄龍警長?\N{\rENG}who thinks he's John Wayne, Rambo, Marshal Dillon?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.53,1:00:34.47,CHT,,0,0,0,,其實我一直崇拜牛仔羅伊\N{\rENG}I was always partial to Roy Rogers, actually.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.10,1:00:36.83,CHT,,0,0,0,,特別是那件亮閃閃的上衣\N{\rENG}I liked those sequined shirts.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.94,1:00:40.17,CHT,,0,0,0,,你真的以為  能和我們對抗嗎  牛仔?\N{\rENG}Do you really think you have a chance against us, Mr Cowboy?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.31,1:00:45.44,CHT,,0,0,0,,等著瞧  混蛋\N{\rENG}Yippee-ki-yay, motherfucker.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.42,1:00:51.51,CHT,,0,0,0,,給我一部新聞車  我能勝過其他人!\N{\rENG}I'll beat everyone if I get a remote.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.59,1:00:53.38,CHT,,0,0,0,,山姆  我還沒拿到新聞稿\N{\rENG}Sam, I don't have the new pages.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.49,1:00:55.72,CHT,,0,0,0,,哈威  保持鎮靜  好嗎?\N{\rENG}Harvey, keep your pants on.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.79,1:00:57.55,CHT,,0,0,0,,山姆  我求你了\N{\rENG}Sam, I'm begging you.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.66,1:01:00.86,CHT,,0,0,0,,西蒙已經乘新聞車出去了  我讓他先去看看\N{\rENG}Simon's with the remote. I'll tell him to swing by.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.96,1:01:02.76,CHT,,0,0,0,,我不想讓給西蒙!\N{\rENG}I won't sit on this!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.86,1:01:05.66,CHT,,0,0,0,,這是我的新聞  我馬上就要去!\N{\rENG}This is my story! I'm going out there!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.73,1:01:07.36,CHT,,0,0,0,,好啦  聽著  山姆  我告訴你\N{\rENG}Look, Sam. Tell you what.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.47,1:01:09.66,CHT,,0,0,0,,如果你不給我一輛車  我就去偷一輛\N{\rENG}You don't give me a truck, I'll steal a truck.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.74,1:01:12.17,CHT,,0,0,0,,嘿  少說兩句  索伯\N{\rENG}- Give us a break, Thornburg. - Eat it, Harvey!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.27,1:01:14.80,CHT,,0,0,0,,-閉嘴  哈威!  -四  三  二...\N{\rENG}four, three, two,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.91,1:01:16.14,CHT,,0,0,0,,一\N{\rENG}one.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.34,1:01:18.11,CHT,,0,0,0,,哈威  已經開始直播了\N{\rENG}Harvey, we're on the air.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.38,1:01:24.48,CHT,,0,0,0,,晚上好  我是哈威·強森\N{\rENG}Good evening. This is Harvey Johnson.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.35,1:01:30.15,CHT,,0,0,0,,我是蓋兒·華倫斯  現在是十點\N{\rENG}And I'm Gail Wallens. This is Nightline News at 10.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.22,1:01:33.02,CHT,,0,0,0,,新聞節目  首先播報要聞\N{\rENG}Our top stories on this Christmas Eve...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.13,1:01:36.29,CHT,,0,0,0,,給你五號車  趕快滾蛋\N{\rENG}Take truck number five and get outta here.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.10,1:01:47.51,CHT,,0,0,0,,他沒騙人  馬可躺在大街上\N{\rENG}He wasn't lying about Marco. He's down on the street.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.57,1:01:49.84,CHT,,0,0,0,,另一個是亨利\N{\rENG}The other man was Heinrich
Dialogue: 0,1:01:49.94,1:01:52.50,CHT,,0,0,0,,他的包不見了\N{\rENG}and his bag is missing.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.98,1:01:56.11,CHT,,0,0,0,,雷管在他那兒\N{\rENG}He had the detonator.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.39,1:02:01.25,CHT,,0,0,0,,西奧\N{\rENG}Theo.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.06,1:02:03.11,CHT,,0,0,0,,西奧\N{\rENG}Theo.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.79,1:02:07.95,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們有麻煩了  你的進展如何?\N{\rENG}We may have some problems. How's our schedule?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:08.56,1:02:10.12,CHT,,0,0,0,,開了三道  還有四道\N{\rENG}Three down, four to go.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:10.20,1:02:11.53,CHT,,0,0,0,,那就別浪費時間和我說話\N{\rENG}Then don't waste time
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.60,1:02:13.46,CHT,,0,0,0,,我是洛杉磯警察局的鮑爾警官\N{\rENG}talking to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.10,1:02:15.73,CHT,,0,0,0,,如果那個報警的人\N{\rENG}This is Sergeant Al Powell
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.80,1:02:18.93,CHT,,0,0,0,,能收到這個頻道\N{\rENG}of the LA Police Department. If the person who radioed for help
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.01,1:02:22.27,CHT,,0,0,0,,請你馬上回話\N{\rENG}can hear me on this channel, acknowledge this transmission.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.38,1:02:23.40,CHT,,0,0,0,,我再說一遍\N{\rENG}I say again,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.48,1:02:26.81,CHT,,0,0,0,,如果剛才報警的人能收到這個頻道\N{\rENG}if the person who radioed for help can hear me,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.88,1:02:29.37,CHT,,0,0,0,,請你馬上回話\N{\rENG}acknowledge this transmission!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.65,1:02:36.28,CHT,,0,0,0,,我聽到了  你就是開車的人?\N{\rENG}I read you, pal. You the guy in the car?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.39,1:02:38.36,CHT,,0,0,0,,那位差點完蛋的\N{\rENG}What's left of him.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.43,1:02:40.05,CHT,,0,0,0,,你能說明身份嗎?\N{\rENG}Can you identify yourself?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.19,1:02:41.85,CHT,,0,0,0,,現在不行  以後再說\N{\rENG}Not now. Maybe later.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.96,1:02:46.02,CHT,,0,0,0,,仔細聽著  頻道上有其他人  他們都喜歡扣扳機\N{\rENG}Listen fast. This is a party line. The neighbors got itchy trigger fingers.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:46.17,1:02:49.60,CHT,,0,0,0,,情況如下  三十層有大約三十名人質\N{\rENG}Here's the deal. You got 30 or so hostages on the 30th floor.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.70,1:02:51.10,CHT,,0,0,0,,匪徒的頭目叫漢斯\N{\rENG}The leader's name is Hans.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.24,1:02:53.87,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們得讓他閉嘴  他什麼都說了\N{\rENG}We have to shut him up. He's telling them everything!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:53.94,1:02:56.03,CHT,,0,0,0,,別管他  我正等著聯邦調查局\N{\rENG}Let him. I'm waiting for the FBI.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.11,1:02:58.24,CHT,,0,0,0,,在那之前  隨便他浪費時間\N{\rENG}He can waste as much time as he likes
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.31,1:03:00.61,CHT,,0,0,0,,不過我們得找到那個背包\N{\rENG}but we must find the bag, Fritz.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.68,1:03:02.71,CHT,,0,0,0,,弗裡茲  去幫尤裡\N{\rENG}They have a freakin' garsenal here.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.82,1:03:04.11,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們必須奪回雷管\N{\rENG}We must have the detonators.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:04.25,1:03:07.80,CHT,,0,0,0,,他們有導彈和自動武器\N{\rENG}They got missiles and enough plastic explosives...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.80,1:03:09.42,CHT,,0,0,0,,炸藥多到能把阿諾德·施瓦辛格炸上天\N{\rENG}to orbit Arnold Schwarzenegger.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.42,1:03:12.26,CHT,,0,0,0,,他們現在還剩九個  算上剛才那位空中飛人\N{\rENG}They're down to nine, counting the skydiver you met.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.33,1:03:17.13,CHT,,0,0,0,,這些人大多數是歐洲人  從他們的服裝...\N{\rENG}These guys are mostly European judging by their clothing labels and...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:23.57,1:03:25.09,CHT,,0,0,0,,和香煙品牌看得出來\N{\rENG}cigarettes.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.24,1:03:27.73,CHT,,0,0,0,,他們手頭富裕  非常專業\N{\rENG}They're well-financed and very slick.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.84,1:03:29.50,CHT,,0,0,0,,你是怎麼知道這些的?\N{\rENG}How do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.58,1:03:31.34,CHT,,0,0,0,,我見過許多假證件\N{\rENG}I've seen enough phony IDs in my time...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.45,1:03:35.28,CHT,,0,0,0,,他們的肯定花了不少錢\N{\rENG}to recognize the ones they got must have cost a fortune.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.55,1:03:39.95,CHT,,0,0,0,,總之  我不知道  這意味著什麼\N{\rENG}Add all that up, I don't know what the fuck it means
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.05,1:03:43.65,CHT,,0,0,0,,但是你們在這兒遇到的  都是職業高手\N{\rENG}but you got some bad-ass perpetrators and they're here to stay.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.19,1:03:48.13,CHT,,0,0,0,,我明白了  老兄  洛杉磯警局的精銳就到了\N{\rENG}I hear you, partner. LA's finest are on it,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.20,1:03:50.16,CHT,,0,0,0,,有時間就抽幾支煙吧\N{\rENG}so light 'em if you got 'em.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.30,1:03:53.06,CHT,,0,0,0,,早就點上了  老兄\N{\rENG}Way ahead of you, partner.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.60,1:03:55.69,CHT,,0,0,0,,我怎麼叫你?\N{\rENG}So what do I call you?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.20,1:03:58.36,CHT,,0,0,0,,叫我...\N{\rENG}Call me...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:00.21,1:04:01.07,CHT,,0,0,0,,羅伊\N{\rENG}Roy.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.14,1:04:04.91,CHT,,0,0,0,,聽我說  羅伊  如果你漏了什麼  千萬別客氣\N{\rENG}Listen up, Roy, if you think of anything else
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.98,1:04:06.14,CHT,,0,0,0,,找一個安全的地方藏起來  其它的事我們來處理  清楚嗎?\N{\rENG}don't be shy, OK?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.21,1:04:09.31,CHT,,0,0,0,,交給你了  艾爾\N{\rENG}In the meantime, find a safe place and let us do ourjob.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.32,1:04:12.58,CHT,,0,0,0,,"一  二  三號鎖解除"\N{\rENG}They're all yours, Al.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.04,1:04:31.37,CHT,,0,0,0,,誰在和他們談判?\N{\rENG}Who's talking to 'em?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.41,1:04:35.43,CHT,,0,0,0,,是我  長官  鮑爾警官  艾爾·鮑爾\N{\rENG}I am, sir. Sergeant Powell. Al Powell.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.91,1:04:39.94,CHT,,0,0,0,,杜恩·羅賓森  怎麼回事?  這些混蛋想要什麼?\N{\rENG}Dwayne Robinson. What's the deal? What do these pricks want?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.01,1:04:42.14,CHT,,0,0,0,,對那些恐怖分子  我們一無所知\N{\rENG}If you mean the terrorists,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:42.22,1:04:44.24,CHT,,0,0,0,,他們什麼也沒說\N{\rENG}we haven't heard a peep from them.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.38,1:04:46.22,CHT,,0,0,0,,那你剛才在和誰通話?\N{\rENG}Who have you been talking to?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:47.25,1:04:50.16,CHT,,0,0,0,,我也不清楚  他不想說他的名字\N{\rENG}We don't know. He won't give us his name.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:50.22,1:04:52.85,CHT,,0,0,0,,但應該就是報警的那個人\N{\rENG}But he appears to be the one who phoned.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.96,1:04:56.19,CHT,,0,0,0,,他殺了一名恐怖分子  而且他說還殺了另外兩個\N{\rENG}He's killed one terrorist and claims he capped two others.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.26,1:04:57.53,CHT,,0,0,0,,他說?\N{\rENG}He claims?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:57.60,1:04:59.79,CHT,,0,0,0,,鮑爾  你有沒有想過...\N{\rENG}Powell, has it occurred to you
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.87,1:05:02.23,CHT,,0,0,0,,是恐怖分子假扮來騙你?\N{\rENG}he could be one of the terrorists...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.34,1:05:04.06,CHT,,0,0,0,,或是什麼瘋子?\N{\rENG}or some nutcase in there?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.17,1:05:07.23,CHT,,0,0,0,,我認為不是  長官  實際上我認為他是員警\N{\rENG}I don't think so. In fact, I think he's a cop,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.34,1:05:10.14,CHT,,0,0,0,,也許不是洛杉磯的  但必是一名員警\N{\rENG}maybe not LAPD, but he's definitely a badge.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.21,1:05:13.48,CHT,,0,0,0,,-你怎麼知道?  -直覺  還有他說的話\N{\rENG}- How do you know that? - A hunch... things he said...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:13.58,1:05:16.34,CHT,,0,0,0,,比如他能分辨假證件\N{\rENG}like being able to spot a phony ID.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:16.45,1:05:18.54,CHT,,0,0,0,,天啊  鮑爾!\N{\rENG}Jesus Christ, Powell!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.62,1:05:21.09,CHT,,0,0,0,,連酒吧的招待都會做!\N{\rENG}He could be a bartender for all we know!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.19,1:05:22.75,CHT,,0,0,0,,記者來了\N{\rENG}TV's here.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.66,1:05:25.25,CHT,,0,0,0,,真糟\N{\rENG}Oh, shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.28,1:05:43.77,CHT,,0,0,0,,我有個要求\N{\rENG}I have a request.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.84,1:05:46.21,CHT,,0,0,0,,哪個笨蛋讓你當老大?\N{\rENG}What idiot put you in charge?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.28,1:05:48.25,CHT,,0,0,0,,就是你\N{\rENG}You did.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.62,1:05:53.51,CHT,,0,0,0,,你殺了我的老闆  現在我最大\N{\rENG}When you murdered my boss. Now everybody's looking to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:53.62,1:05:58.72,CHT,,0,0,0,,我並不想要這個責任  因為我不想這麼靠近你\N{\rENG}Personally, I'd pass on the job. I don't enjoy being this close to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.70,1:06:08.00,CHT,,0,0,0,,說吧\N{\rENG}Go on.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.10,1:06:10.07,CHT,,0,0,0,,外面有一位懷孕的婦女\N{\rENG}We have a pregnant woman.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.14,1:06:13.07,CHT,,0,0,0,,放心  她還有幾周才會生\N{\rENG}Relax. She's not due for a couple of weeks...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:13.14,1:06:16.30,CHT,,0,0,0,,但是坐在地板上對她的背不好\N{\rENG}but sitting on that rock isn't doing her any good.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.41,1:06:20.71,CHT,,0,0,0,,請你准許讓她到  辦公室的沙發上坐\N{\rENG}So I would like permission to move her to an office with a sofa.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:21.68,1:06:24.62,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們可以把沙發搬出來  不是嗎?\N{\rENG}No, but I'll have a sofa brought out. Good enough?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.68,1:06:26.45,CHT,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\rENG}Good enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.55,1:06:31.86,CHT,,0,0,0,,如果你怕髒的話  最好開始讓我們分組去上廁所\N{\rENG}And unless you like it messy, I'd start bringing us in groups to the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:32.29,1:06:35.69,CHT,,0,0,0,,對  你說的對  沒問題\N{\rENG}Yes. You're right. It will be done.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:36.50,1:06:37.62,CHT,,0,0,0,,還有別的事嗎?\N{\rENG}Was there something else?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.03,1:06:42.02,CHT,,0,0,0,,沒有  謝謝\N{\rENG}No, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:48.07,1:06:51.73,CHT,,0,0,0,,青木先生很會選人  你是...\N{\rENG}Mr Takagi chose his people well, Mrs?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.84,1:06:53.90,CHT,,0,0,0,,吉奈蘿\N{\rENG}Gennero.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:54.84,1:06:57.14,CHT,,0,0,0,,吉奈蘿小姐\N{\rENG}Ms Gennero.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.78,1:07:02.37,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們中斷節目  播出特別新聞報導\N{\rENG}We interrupt this program for a special bulletin.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.48,1:07:05.98,CHT,,0,0,0,,理查·索伯在世紀城  為您現場報導\N{\rENG}This is Richard Thornburg live from Century City.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.45,1:07:11.72,CHT,,0,0,0,,今晚  洛杉磯也成為...\N{\rENG}Tonight, Los Angeles has joined the sad and worldwide fraternity of cities
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.79,1:07:13.78,CHT,,0,0,0,,遭受國際恐怖分子威脅的\N{\rENG}whose only membership requirement...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.89,1:07:16.95,CHT,,0,0,0,,全球城市之列\N{\rENG}is to suffer the anguish of international terrorism.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.06,1:07:21.40,CHT,,0,0,0,,大約兩個小時以前  一群身份不詳的恐怖分子\N{\rENG}Approximately two hours ago, an unidentified group of men...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.50,1:07:26.50,CHT,,0,0,0,,佔領了中富大廈  封鎖了所有入口和出口\N{\rENG}seized control of the Nakatomi building, sealing off all entrances and exits.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:26.61,1:07:30.91,CHT,,0,0,0,,電話線全部被切斷  現在唯一的通訊手段\N{\rENG}All telephone lines have been cut and the only communication now possible
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.98,1:07:33.91,CHT,,0,0,0,,就是無線電對講機\N{\rENG}has been through the use of CB communicators...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:33.98,1:07:36.35,CHT,,0,0,0,,顯然是由恐怖分子帶來的\N{\rENG}which the group brought with them.
